{"tid":1395092,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（突破夢中封鎖）思考香城online物資短缺應如何面對","createTime":"2019-08-01T15:43:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T16:11:22.000Z","uid":263218,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a33a1c899d4bf8aea81ecc703c1c9302c5b714f3","tid":1395092,"uid":263218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:43:59.000Z","msg":"先講現象，再講分析建議<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現象局面<br />\n<br />\n1. 前線物資情況比以往感到短缺<br />\n<br />\n2. 狗仔清倉偷貨 <br />\n<br />\n3. 淘寶斷貨斷供應，對香港地區設限制<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n分析：<br />\n<br />\n1. 香港欠缺工業產業發展，靠外面引進始終無法無法自強，連口罩都要靠進口。香港人要全面反思農業、工業的發展。<br />\n<br />\n2.  狗仔斷你貨，香港人要搵出路，如果唔係 唔知10月仲有冇得堅持<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n建議<br />\n<br />\n1. 突破淘寶封鎖，或需靠澳門幫手<br />\n<br />\n2. 開拓其他國家支援，有勞商人引入台貨、越貨 （美貨真係好能貴）<br />\n<br />\n3. 其他？等大家建議"},{"pid":"33e5f8b6b6121cec9490debb8ef18cb916b3a4b4","tid":1395092,"uid":269681,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:48:55.000Z","msg":"向隔離台服搵下幫手得唔得"},{"pid":"3c10c25eab88bfee47934bf710b0f8ab8cde2ea4","tid":1395092,"uid":263218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:50:48.000Z","msg":"集思廣益"},{"pid":"82ba2c8bdae7b7e43e8e2d97fa82b13e73d5e7ab","tid":1395092,"uid":263218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:54:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"072f939d85447c191d88dc62a9c6f0adeb9d2dd7","tid":1395092,"uid":263218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:54:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8e36af427c24961da7b0e9443f4a60aa4f03769c","tid":1395092,"uid":16468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:54:47.000Z","msg":"amazon"},{"pid":"5c4e3339194ff1fb9d0cd0184656e55ad44039fc","tid":1395092,"uid":69125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:55:01.000Z","msg":"物資分散拎,每人拎d"},{"pid":"9994fa3218349c1a5aad6f81785e6e8aea53dfb3","tid":1395092,"uid":53803,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T15:55:01.000Z"